.000Z","msg":"Ching<br />\n留返條命星五衝左先<br />\n忍唔到個死柒婆 開記招當同fd吹水甘"},{"pid":"e83987506a85837ee07bd75693cdb7320ed90cb0","tid":1240024,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0856f239dceb5ea92573759616de9a10f978d2b","tid":1240024,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"ching 係自己身邊發生咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a990cbd1f98a4b1b7c67b0c6ff45bab6eab39b5","tid":1240024,"uid":234788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0856f239dceb5ea92573759616de9a10f978d2b","tid":1240024,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"唔知之後點真係好辛苦，日日都好似好被動咁俾個環境操控住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得睇唔清楚前面環境，<br />\n與其一頭向前衝，真係要停一停，甚至向後行幾步，離開下個環境，<br />\n可能有機會睇闊D又搵到出路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊撐住呀！！！"},{"pid":"f69dda62999b188bfecb8d7692685f54c162ba5f","tid":1240024,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"試下自我增值"},{"pid":"bc3c11264f6a0ab3f395e568ce5128cb728e2f61","tid":1240024,"uid":162744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"有人同我講過，無論條路點黑，最後係點都會有光明。<br />\n我認同，只係過程中會有好多難關，加油，我同你都係一樣。"},{"pid":"c2fb32e1abb74290a8449906c573fe5d06f4e1a6","tid":1240024,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:15:37.000Z","msg":"失學 失業 失戀(未戀先失個隻）(追過我post就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n同屋企人關係唔好<br />\n想搵人傾，打開friend完全唔知可以搵邊個，唔想打搞人，係我問題我煩膠我鑽牛角尖我唔睇開啲，我根本唔值得人為我好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報左ive同一科3年 今日派位繼續nothing<br />\n完全唔知前面自己應該點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住香港咁 有心無力 <br />\n個個遊行行完當做左野 繼續歌舞昇平 唔關佢事<br />\n好唔甘心 好嬲 但咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n好想做第二個烈士 <br />\n起碼我一事無成既人生有番啲意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9e18c485d9f67868e0b85e8bc9e2b3f221bdaf","tid":1240024,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a990cbd1f98a4b1b7c67b0c6ff45bab6eab39b5","tid":1240024,"uid":234788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0856f239dceb5ea92573759616de9a10f978d2b","tid":1240024,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"唔知之後點真係好辛苦，日日都好似好被動咁俾個環境操控住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得睇唔清楚前面環境，<br />\n與其一頭向前衝，真係要停一停，甚至向後行幾步，離開下個環境，<br />\n可能有機會睇闊D又搵到出路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊撐住呀！！！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"上星期啱啱一個人去完台灣番黎，<br />\n諗住過去散下心 抖下會好啲，<br />\n點知撞到正69 612，<br />\n野食唔落 覺瞓唔到 日日拎住電話連登追post，<br />\n夜晚內疚自責到係民宿喊到天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361b840006dfa0842f356d65d60f38d5e135cf3f","tid":1240024,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"抗爭繼續  你走去生無可戀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b221a6634bb23b948bbc2c0499df2adef62c42","tid":1240024,"uid":119858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2